{"id":"683174826","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:78eff0a4-aa6a-43bc-bf03-ad8ced3bf6ad:page/683174826","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NzhlZmYwYTQtYWE2YS00M2JjLWJmMDMtYWQ4Y2VkM2JmNmFkOmNvbnRlbnQvNjgzMTc0ODI2","status":"current","title":"[사양서] Focus / Select","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"712020:007b5010-0b14-479a-a922-0efb123d181a","accountType":"atlassian","email":"woo_mary@pubg.com","publicName":"Seongyeong Woo (우선경)","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/712020:007b5010-0b14-479a-a922-0efb123d181a","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"Seongyeong Woo (우선경)","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"ko","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=712020:007b5010-0b14-479a-a922-0efb123d181a"}},"when":"2025-07-28T08:39:41.714Z","friendlyWhen":"7월 28, 2025","message":"","number":3,"minorEdit":false,"ncsStepVersion":"1820","ncsStepVersionSource":"ncs-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$683174826.14","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/683174826"},"_links":{"self":"https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/683174826/version/3"}},"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p /><h1>정의 </h1><p> <ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"e10cb38b-775d-4b9e-8ed9-193cdf26728f\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">elements</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro>  아웃게임에서의 포커싱/호버 상태와 셀렉트를 확인 할 수 있는 2px의 라인 박스</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"355\" ac:original-width=\"913\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:alt=\"image-20250728-083319.png\" ac:width=\"760\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20250728-083319.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><h1>UX Guide<br /></h1><ul><li><p>Focus (Console)  : 포커스 상태를 표시</p></li><li><p>Hover (PC) : 마우스 호버 시 호버 액션으로 사용 가능함</p></li><li><p>Select (PC/Console) : 선택 상태의 UI를 보여줌</p></li></ul><h1>Spec</h1><ul><li><p>동일 선상에서는 Focus 규칙에 따라 Select 보다 상위에 Focus 라인이 위치합니다.</p></li></ul><h1>Property</h1><ul><li><p><em><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(76,154,255);\">이미지</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(76,154,255);\">를 최대한 잘 활용해서 넣자</span></em></p></li><li><p><em><span style=\"color: rgb(76,154,255);\">의도 설명 불필요, 스펙만 나열</span></em></p></li><li><p><em><span style=\"color: rgb(76,154,255);\">아무것도 정의하지 않았을 때 기본값으로 노출되는 상태에 </span></em><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"e5fd65fd-e1f3-4879-b170-2266e4a71cc8\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">default</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro><span style=\"color: rgb(76,154,255);\">  </span><em><span style=\"color: rgb(76,154,255);\">표시</span></em></p></li></ul><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"6d3db7a1-28af-4ce7-8a54-acc4da38d9d1\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>자세한 스펙은 아래 링크로 확인 가능합니다.</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://ordo.pubg.io/?path=/story/functional-coach-mark--coach-mark\">Story Book</a> (아직 배포 전이라면 TBD)</p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/c8Qux8CARpdsaKg1KsUwMm/-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5--ORDO-Design-system?node-id=386-445\">ORDO Figma</a></p></li></ul></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"center\" ac:local-id=\"29a7922a-80cc-4450-8034-8e472adadce1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 165.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 160.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 432.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>속성 / 구분</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>타입</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>설명</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>종류 (Type)</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Focus <ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"a186332a-0239-49bb-b9e4-f4bedd5fe730\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">default</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro>    </p></li><li><p>Hover</p></li><li><p>Select</p></li></ul></td><td><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"674\" ac:original-width=\"1422\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:alt=\"image-20250728-082845.png\" ac:width=\"417\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20250728-082845.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></td></tr></tbody></table><h1>적용 케이스</h1><p>본 컴포넌트가 적용된 사례를 리스트업합니다.</p><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"align-start\" ac:local-id=\"4b07bcb3-01db-4330-8138-1aa44133ade1\"><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>경로</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>이미지</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>설명</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Hideout - Contraband</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><h1>예외 케이스</h1><p>본 컴포넌트를 사용하지 않고 변형 적용한 사례를 기록해둡니다.</p><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"align-start\" ac:local-id=\"562ab08c-8eef-43f3-a554-5c6a4311fe10\"><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>경로</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>이미지</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>설명</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Hideout - Contraband</p></td><td><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1096\" ac:original-width=\"2225\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:alt=\"image-20250728-083806.png\" ac:width=\"236\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20250728-083806.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /></td><td><p>좌측 배너의 Select 상태가 노란 라인으로 나오고있습니다. (별도의 디자인)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><h1>수정 로그</h1><ul><li><p><time datetime=\"2025-07-23\" /> </p><ul><li><p><ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"inline\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"#38.1 - 콘솔 포커스 조작 확장\" ri:version-at-save=\"7\" /><ac:link-body>#38.1 - 콘솔 포커스 조작 확장</ac:link-body></ac:link> </p></li><li><p>기존 12개의 타입으로 나뉜 포커스 스타일을 38.1 기준으로 인라인 2px 상태만 남김</p></li><li><p>포커스와 동일한 라인의 셀렉트 상태를 Focus 컴포넌트에 추가하여 함께 관리할 수 있도록 추가</p></li></ul></li></ul><p /><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/683174826"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":981571384},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/PUBGOutGame","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/683174826/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/683174826/history","descendants":"/rest/api/content/683174826/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/PUBGOutGame","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/683174826/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=683174826","webui":"/spaces/PUBGOutGame/pages/683174826/Focus+Select","edituiv2":"/spaces/PUBGOutGame/pages/edit-v2/683174826","context":"/wiki","self":"https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/683174826","tinyui":"/x/qmu4K","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki"}}